name: TCLee
tagline: Hello, brave adventurer. Welcome to my GitHub Page.
body:
##iOS Projects

[TCGoogleStreetView](http://tclee.github.io/TCGoogleStreetView) - Visit museums using Google Street View.

[TCGoogleMaps](http://tclee.github.io/TCGoogleMaps) - Get driving directions with Google Maps.

[TCPhotos500px](http://tclee.github.io/TCPhotos500px) - Explore the best of 500px's photos.

[TCKnowledgeGraph](http://tclee.github.io/TCKnowledgeGraph) - Learning with Freebase's knowledge graph.

[TCParticleFX](https://github.com/TCLee/TCParticleFX) - Easy particle effects with Core Animation.

[TCFaceDetection](https://github.com/TCLee/TCFaceDetection) - Detect a person' face in a photo and automatically enhance the photo using Core Image.

[TCImageFilter](https://github.com/TCLee/TCImageFilter) - Experimenting with Core Image's filters.

[TCMusicPlayer](https://github.com/TCLee/TCMusicPlayer) - Build your very own music player with Apple's `AV Foundation` classes.

##Mac OS X Projects

[Google Books Downloader](https://github.com/TCLee/GoogleBooksDownloader/) - Download preview pages from Google Books for your offline reading pleasure.
